{"tid":1721495,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"簽署L: 鍾雅倫呢單仲欠好多，快D幫下手","createTime":"2019-11-14T16:14:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-16T10:53:57.000Z","uid":270025,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d5b4099aa3aa9aefb7192f386d8aee7c052f7796","tid":1721495,"uid":270025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T16:14:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/launch-tax-investigation-us-citizen-nga-lun-chung-who-serves-superintendent-police-hong-kong\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Flaunch-tax-investigation-us-citizen-nga-lun-chung-who-serves-superintendent-police-hong-kong&d=zfTWtzkQ24d%2FEmJzkWMc69XdGXproJJDEW77mXnEmng%3D&h=2db803f6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/launch-tax-investigation-us-citizen-nga-lun-chung-who-serves-superintendent-police-hong-kong</a><br />\n<br />\n三步曲: 1. Sign 2. Email自己確認 3. 分享比所有人<br />\n<br />\n昨日（13日）在紅磡拘捕孕婦的警員又是美國籍 #鍾雅倫 警司。本媒較早前發起白宮聯署呼籲美國查稅，現在簽署還要六萬人，5日後就完結，大家是不是想放過鍾警司？請幫手分享到各大群組及論壇。<br />\n<br />\n警司起身點50-53，假設 #鍾雅倫 警司的起身點為50，即每月人工HKD116,355，年薪1,396,260（不包括超時補薪及房屋津貼）。<br />\n<br />\n美國實行全球徵稅，美國籍人士，包括綠卡持有人，即使不在美國工作及生活，依然要每年向美國報稅及交稅，徵稅範圍包括薪酬、股息、投資盈利、退休金、遺產等。<br />\n<br />\n本媒粗略幫計算過，2018年鍾警司要向美國政府繳交USD45,686（只根據年薪計算，實際金額要視乎家庭狀況、其他收入及海外人士免稅額），不知道鍾警司有沒有準時交稅呢？<br />\n<br />\n鍾警司在香港高薪厚職，而且貴人善忘，為免鍾警司忘記向美國當局交稅，本媒發起 #白宮聯署，要求 #美國稅務局落案調查：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/launch-tax-investigation-us-citizen-nga-lun-chung-who-serves-superintendent-police-hong-kong\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Flaunch-tax-investigation-us-citizen-nga-lun-chung-who-serves-superintendent-police-hong-kong&d=zfTWtzkQ24d%2FEmJzkWMc69XdGXproJJDEW77mXnEmng%3D&h=2db803f6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/launch-tax-investigation-us-citizen-nga-lun-chung-who-serves-superintendent-police-hong-kong</a><br />\n<br />\n請大家廣傳及簽署✍🏻<br />\n<br />\n鍾雅倫逮捕孕婦精彩片段 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/113518510028109/posts/148585289854764?vh=e&amp;d=n&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F113518510028109%2Fposts%2F148585289854764%3Fvh%3De%26d%3Dn%26sfns%3Dmo&d=zfTWtzkQ24d%2FEmJzkWMc69XdGXproJJDEW77mXnEmng%3D&h=0e46fcf4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/113518510028109/posts/148585289854764?vh=e&amp;d=n&amp;sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"5e7bc0e41262f8d6a551d025b1c9c543434d9be8","tid":1721495,"uid":270025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T04:39:01.000Z","msg":"push 1 push"},{"pid":"6f724601882f1867a38541f9488fe670ce77eded","tid":1721495,"uid":270025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T10:53:57.000Z","msg":"push 1 push"}]}